Usage: jpipe run [options]

Execute the data processing engine with the following configurations:

Options:
  -c, --chunk-size <size>    Buffer size (e.g., 512kb, 16mb). Range: 1kb-64mb  (default: 1kb)
  -b, --backlog    <count>   Max pending operations. Range: 1-1024 (default: 1)
  -o, --out-dir    <path>    Output directory.
  -h, --help                 Show this help message.
